  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A multi-part study to evaluate the safety and PK of single ascending doses of IDX21549 in
      healthy and HCV-infected subjects. The effect of food on the PK of IDX21549 will also be
      evaluated. Antiviral activity will also be assessed in HCV-infected subjects.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <overall_status>Terminated</overall_status>
  <why_stopped>
    Early termination of IDX21459 was due to integration of Merck's HCV antiviral pipeline has
    resulted in revisions of the clinical development plan.
  </why_stopped>
